&lt;DIV&gt;If you feel no need to play a CHARACTER then skip the whole business altogether. The Dragons are the evil as well as the muramites. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Bottom line imay need to do thirty missions to get the aa for a particular faction but i can do any of the shared missions and turn in my tokens if i choose while still not being able to set foot in their camp/ Thats certainly something none of us have been able to do before and it is a luxury to be able to do so without the mindless&amp;nbsp; faction killing of green of&amp;nbsp; days past. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;instead of moaning how your immediately kos to one faction and have to be able to work your way up in faction . You should be glad there is a way your character can betray its race and deity&amp;nbsp; and serve the other side&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
